Hola!!!
I am Vamika. I am an Interdisciplinary Scientist and Industry Expert. I am on a mission to help
100,000 learners experience the pleasure of Gamified Learning. I am the founder of Creasemble,
a game design hub. I believe in the formula of learning by doing and interacting, and I am a
proud creator of games across domains.
We are here because:
1
Dry and difficult things fail to capture the learner’s imagination and interest
2
Low cost alternatives to address the digital divide and also need for digital detox
Missed opportunities due to shortage and subpar quality of teaching resources
3
Optimality.
